summary: Along with ChizFoShiz's voiceset mod, this will make you sound like a female child in Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
-NEEDS VOICESET MOD, check it out!-
<br />VOICESET MOD http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51387/?tab=2&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D51387&pUp=1
<br />
<br />It's been a long time since my last custom voiceset upload. This is a custom voiceset that makes your character sound like the default Skyrim female child. 
<br />There is no real point in trying to contact me as I am not active and only drop things off once in a while, when I make them for myself and decide that others may like them. So, I am just dropping off a stock version of this voiceset. Feel free to edit it and redistribute.
<br />Goes along great with child race mods!
<br />
<br />My Dremora Voiceset: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52727/?
author: pwnlink3
